sd=Customer Behavioral Insights	This service domain applies behavioral analysis to customer event history to maintain a range of customer ratings/scores (such as 'propensity to buy') and to detect life events or trends	A regular analysis of customer event histories is used to update the maintained range of customer behavioral insights. The updated results are notified to the Customer Relationship Management and Party Profile Service Domains as appropriate	This service domain references the range of customer historical data maintained by the Customer Event History service domain to develop behavioral insights into customers. This analysis can support sales and marketing activity (e.g. by determining the likely response to sales efforts based on passed performance) as well as identifying changes in status and behavior that might influence the desired product mix for a customer. The actual analysis routines are developed/maintained by the Customer Behavior Models service domain
sdpath=customer-behavioral-insights
crpath=customer-behavior-analysis
crr=Customer Behavior Analysis Instance
mcr=Customer Behavior Analysis
bqs=Insight
CONFIG
CustomerBehaviorAnalysis	evaluate	Set-up evaluation of customer behavior insights for a customer		evaluateCustomerBehaviorAnalysis		#desc
CustomerBehaviorAnalysis	exchange	Accept, verify, etc. customer behavior insights		exchangeCustomerBehaviorAnalysis		#desc
CustomerBehaviorAnalysis	execute	Execute an automated task for customer insights (e.g. automated refresh		executeCustomerBehaviorAnalysis		#desc
CustomerBehaviorAnalysis	request	Request manual intervention for customer insights (e.g. unscheduled revision)		requestCustomerBehaviorAnalysis		#desc
CustomerBehaviorAnalysis	retrieve	Retrieve details about customer behavior insights		retrieveCustomerBehaviorAnalysis		#desc
Insight	exchange	Accept, verify etc. a selected type of customer behavior insight	exchangeCustomerBehaviorAnalysisInsight	exchangeCustomerBehaviorAnalysisInsight		Handle an external exchange (e.g. accept, reject, verify)
Insight	execute	Execute an automated task for a specific customer behavior insight (e.g. refresh)	executeCustomerBehaviorAnalysisInsight	executeCustomerBehaviorAnalysisInsight		Invoke an automated execute action against the Insight instance
Insight	request	Request manual intervention for a specific customer behavior insight (e.g. re-calculate)	requestCustomerBehaviorAnalysisInsight	requestCustomerBehaviorAnalysisInsight		Invoke a service request action against the Insight instance
Insight	retrieve	Retrieve details about a specific customer behavior insight	retrieveCustomerBehaviorAnalysisInsight	retrieveCustomerBehaviorAnalysisInsight		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Insight instance related report